---
description: Prisma 7 schema, migrations, and client generation
globs: apps/api/prisma/**/*,prisma.config.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

# Prisma 7

- **No `url` in `schema.prisma`** — connection string lives in root `prisma.config.ts`.
- Generator: `provider = "prisma-client"`, `output = "../src/generated/prisma"`.
- After schema changes: `pnpm prisma:generate` then add migration SQL under `apps/api/prisma/migrations/`.
- Seed: `apps/api/prisma/seed.ts` uses `PrismaPg` + generated client (same as `PrismaService`).
- Do not hand-edit generated files under `apps/api/src/generated/`.
